TEXT(&beginproblem);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Complete the following equation.  Your answers will be algebraic expressions.

$BR 
\((a+b i)^2=\) \{ ans_rule(5) \} \(+\)
EOT
&ANS(multivar_function_cmp("a**2-b**2",["a","b"]));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
\{ ans_rule(5) \} \(i\)
EOT
&ANS(multivar_function_cmp("2*a*b",["a","b"]));

TEXT(EV3(<<'EOT'));
$BR Hint: Think of \(i\) as an ordinary variable and then 
replace \(i^2\) with \(-1\).
EOT

SOLUTION(EV3(<<'EOT'));
$BR $BBOLD Solution:$EBOLD
\[(a+bi)^2 = a^2 +2abi + b^2i^2 = \left(a^2-b^2\right) + \left(2ab\right)i.\]
EOT


